Writing again about the new add sheet. I'm really fond of it, and the ability to create multiple issues in sequence is really nice. However, it seems odd to have a 2-step process (click the Create Another, then click Create) seems unnecessary for a feature designed for efficiency. It would make more sense to have just a button that performs the steps.

