  {panel}

http://confluence.atlassian.com/display/JIRA/Setting+your+JIRA+Home+Directory suggests to configure the file manually. The file says 'Do not modify this file unless instructed'. 

We should change the documentation to use the recommended method of running config.sh or config.bat.

